You are a police officer. A maniac has planted a bomb next to a public fountain.

To defuse the bomb, you must solve a puzzle. The puzzle is solved when you fill any of the available jugs with the target amount of water.

You have three move types: 'fill', 'empty' and 'pour'.

To fill Jug A, you 'fill A'.
To empty Jug B, you 'empty B'.
To pour the contents of Jug A into Jug B, you 'pour A->B'.
All jugs are empty to begin with.

The empty jugs hold this many litres of water: A:11, B:12, C:12, D:12
And your target is: 4 litres.

How do you defuse the bomb?

Reply as a JSON-parsable list of moves which result in any of the jugs being filled with the target amount.

results.question:
You are a police officer. A maniac has planted a bomb next to a public fountain.

To defuse the bomb, you must solve a puzzle. The puzzle is solved when you fill any of the available jugs with the target amount of water.

You have three move types: 'fill', 'empty' and 'pour'.

To fill Jug A, you 'fill A'.
To empty Jug B, you 'empty B'.
To pour the contents of Jug A into Jug B, you 'pour A->B'.
All jugs are empty to begin with.

The empty jugs hold this many litres of water: A:13, B:7, C:13, D:7
And your target is: 9 litres.

How do you defuse the bomb?

Reply as a JSON-parsable list of moves which result in any of the jugs being filled with the target amount.

To defuse the bomb, you must solve a puzzle. The puzzle is solved when you fill any of the available jugs with the target amount of water.

You have three move types: 'fill', 'empty' and 'pour'.

To fill Jug A, you 'fill A'.
To empty Jug B, you 'empty B'.
To pour the contents of Jug A into Jug B, you 'pour A->B'.
All jugs are empty to begin with.

The empty jugs hold this many litres of water: A:8, B:13, C:5, D:13
And your target is: 9 litres.

How do you defuse the bomb?

Reply as a JSON-parsable list of moves which result in any of the jugs being filled with the target amount.

7. **Fill jug A:** This refills jug A with 8 liters.
8. **Pour A into B:** This fills jug B completely (13 liters) and leaves 9 liters in jug A.

To defuse the bomb, you must solve a puzzle. The puzzle is solved when you fill any of the available jugs with the target amount of water.

You have three move types: 'fill', 'empty' and 'pour'.

To fill Jug A, you 'fill A'.
To empty Jug B, you 'empty B'.

All jugs are empty to begin with.

And your target is: 4 litres.

results.question:
You are a police officer. A maniac has planted a bomb next to a public fountain.

To defuse the bomb, you must solve a puzzle. The puzzle is solved when you fill any of the available jugs with the target amount of water.

You have three move types: 'fill', 'empty' and 'pour'.

To fill Jug A, you 'fill A'.
To empty Jug B, you 'empty B'.
To pour the contents of Jug A into Jug B, you 'pour A->B'.
All jugs are empty to begin with.

The empty jugs hold this many litres of water: A:13, B:13, C:4, D:13
And your target is: 6 litres.

How do you defuse the bomb?

Reply as a JSON-parsable list of moves which result in any of the jugs being filled with the target amount.
results.expected_answer: ["fill A", "pour A->C", "fill B", "empty C", "pour A->C", "empty C", "pour A->C", "empty C", "pour A->C", "pour B->C", "empty C", "pour B->C"]

results.question:
You are a police officer. A maniac has planted a bomb next to a public fountain.

To defuse the bomb, you must solve a puzzle. The puzzle is solved when you fill any of the available jugs with the target amount of water.

You have three move types: 'fill', 'empty' and 'pour'.

To fill Jug A, you 'fill A'.
To empty Jug B, you 'empty B'.
To pour the contents of Jug A into Jug B, you 'pour A->B'.
All jugs are empty to begin with.

The empty jugs hold this many litres of water: A:13, B:12, C:12, D:12
And your target is: 8 litres.

How do you defuse the bomb?

Reply as a JSON-parsable list of moves which result in any of the jugs being filled with the target amount.
results.expected_answer: ["fill B", "pour B->A", "fill B", "pour B->A", "empty A", "pour B->A", "fill B", "pour B->A", "empty A", "pour B->A", "fill B", "pour B->A", "empty A", "pour B->A", "fill B", "pour B->A"]

results.question:
You are a police officer. A maniac has planted a bomb next to a public fountain.

To defuse the bomb, you must solve a puzzle. The puzzle is solved when you fill any of the available jugs with the target amount of water.

You have three move types: 'fill', 'empty' and 'pour'.

To fill Jug A, you 'fill A'.
To empty Jug B, you 'empty B'.
To pour the contents of Jug A into Jug B, you 'pour A->B'.
All jugs are empty to begin with.

The empty jugs hold this many litres of water: A:5, B:13, C:13, D:5
And your target is: 4 litres.

How do you defuse the bomb?

Reply as a JSON-parsable list of moves which result in any of the jugs being filled with the target amount.
results.expected_answer: ["fill A", "pour A->B", "fill A", "pour A->B", "fill A", "pour A->B", "pour A->C", "fill A", "pour A->C", "fill A", "pour A->C", "fill A", "pour A->C"]

results.question:
You are a police officer. A maniac has planted a bomb next to a public fountain.

To defuse the bomb, you must solve a puzzle. The puzzle is solved when you fill any of the available jugs with the target amount of water.

You have three move types: 'fill', 'empty' and 'pour'.

To fill Jug A, you 'fill A'.
To empty Jug B, you 'empty B'.
To pour the contents of Jug A into Jug B, you 'pour A->B'.
All jugs are empty to begin with.

The empty jugs hold this many litres of water: A:11, B:6, C:11, D:6
And your target is: 3 litres.

How do you defuse the bomb?

Reply as a JSON-parsable list of moves which result in any of the jugs being filled with the target amount.

results.question:
You are a police officer. A maniac has planted a bomb next to a public fountain.

To defuse the bomb, you must solve a puzzle. The puzzle is solved when you fill any of the available jugs with the target amount of water.

You have three move types: 'fill', 'empty' and 'pour'.

To fill Jug A, you 'fill A'.
To empty Jug B, you 'empty B'.
To pour the contents of Jug A into Jug B, you 'pour A->B'.
All jugs are empty to begin with.

The empty jugs hold this many litres of water: A:11, B:5, C:11, D:11
And your target is: 3 litres.

How do you defuse the bomb?

Reply as a JSON-parsable list of moves which result in any of the jugs being filled with the target amount.
results.expected_answer: ["fill B", "pour B->A", "fill B", "pour B->A", "fill B", "pour B->A", "pour B->C", "pour A->B", "pour B->C", "pour A->B", "pour B->C"]

results.question:
You are a police officer. A maniac has planted a bomb next to a public fountain.

To defuse the bomb, you must solve a puzzle. The puzzle is solved when you fill any of the available jugs with the target amount of water.

You have three move types: 'fill', 'empty' and 'pour'.

To fill Jug A, you 'fill A'.
To empty Jug B, you 'empty B'.
To pour the contents of Jug A into Jug B, you 'pour A->B'.
All jugs are empty to begin with.

The empty jugs hold this many litres of water: A:11, B:12, C:11, D:12
And your target is: 4 litres.

How do you defuse the bomb?

Reply as a JSON-parsable list of moves which result in any of the jugs being filled with the target amount.
